# Kotlin to Java

```java
void updateWeather(int degree) {
  String description;
  Color color;
  if (degree < 10) {
    description = "cold";
    color = Color.BLUE;
  } else if (degree < 25) {
    description = "mild";
    color = Color.ORANGE;    
  } else {
    description = "hot";
    color = Color.RED;    
  }
}
```


```kotlin

fun updateWeather(degree: Int) {
    var (description : String, color : Color) = when {
        degree < 10 -> "cold" to Color.BLUE
        degree < 25 -> "mild" to Color.ORANGE
        else -> "hot" to Color.RED
    }
}

```
